amp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20US%20Troops%20Killed%20In%20Drone%20Attack%20In%20Jordan%20Amid%20Israel-Hamas%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20drone%20attack%20on%20a%20base%20in%20Jordan%20killed%20three%20American%20troops%20on%20Sunday%2C%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20blaming%20Iran-backed%20militants%20and%20vowing%20to%20hold%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20time%20American%20military%20personnel%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20hostile%20fire%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%2C%20and%20the%20incident%20will%20further%20raise%20tensions%20in%20the%20region%20and%20fuel%20fears%20of%20a%20broader%20conflict%20directly%20involving%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20the%20death%20of%20the%20soldiers%20shows%20Washington's%20backing%20for%20Israel%20could%20put%20it%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20whole%20Muslim%20world%20if%20the%20Gaza%20war%20continues%20and%20that%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bregional%20explosion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20are%20still%20gathering%20the%20facts%20of%20this%20attack%2C%20we%20know%20it%20was%20carried%20out%20by%20radical%20Iran-backed%20militant%20groups%20operating%20in%20Syria%20and%20Iraq%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHold%20perpetrators%20'to%20account'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20carry%20on%20their%20commitment%20to%20fight%20terrorism.%20And%20have%20no%20doubt%20--%20we%20will%20hold%20all%20those%20responsible%20to%20account%20at%20a%20time%20and%20in%20a%20manner%20of%20our%20choosing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20Central%20Command%20put%20the%20number%20of%20wounded%20from%20the%20attack%20near%20the%20Syrian%20border%20at%2025%2C%20and%20said%20the%20identities%20of%20those%20killed%20will%20be%20withheld%20pending%20notification%20of%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20spokesman%20Sami%20Abu%20Zuhri%20said%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20soldiers%20%26quot%3Bis%20a%20message%20to%20the%20American%20administration%20that%20unless%20the%20killing%20of%20innocent%20people%20in%20Gaza%20stops%2C%20it%20may%20be%20faced%20with%20the%20entire%20(Muslim)%20nation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20continuation%20of%20the%20American-Zionist%20aggression%20on%20Gaza%20risks%20a%20regional%20explosion%2C%26quot%3B%20Abu%20Zuhri%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20and%20allied%20forces%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%20have%20been%20targeted%20in%20more%20than%20150%20attacks%20since%20mid-October%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20and%20Washington%20has%20carried%20out%20retaliatory%20strikes%20in%20both%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20attacks%20on%20US%20personnel%20have%20been%20claimed%20by%20the%20Islamic%20Resistance%20in%20Iraq%2C%20a%20loose%20alliance%20of%20Iran-linked%20armed%20groups%20that%20oppose%20US%20support%20for%20Israel%20in%20the%20Gaza%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20round%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20began%20when%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20carried%20out%20a%20shock%20attack%20on%20October%207%20that%20resulted%20in%20about%201%2C140%20deaths%2C%20mostly%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20an%20AFP%20tally%20of%20official%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrowing%20Middle%20East%20crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20United%20States%20rushed%20military%20aid%20to%20Israel%2C%20which%20has%20carried%20out%20a%20relentless%20military%20offensive%20that%20has%20killed%20at%20least%2026%2C422%20people%20in%20Gaza%2C%20most%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Gaza%20health%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20deaths%20have%20sparked%20widespread%20anger%20across%20the%20region%20and%20stoked%20violence%20involving%20Iran-backed%20groups%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%20as%20well%20as%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lebanon%20portion%20of%20the%20conflict%20has%20been%20limited%20to%20near%20daily%20exchanges%20of%20fire%20between%20Hezbollah%20and%20Israel%2C%20but%20American%20forces%20are%20directly%20involved%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYemen's%20Iran-backed%20Huthi%20rebels%20have%20carried%20out%20more%20than%20two%20months%20of%20attacks%20on%20shipping%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20hitting%20Israeli-linked%20vessels%20in%20support%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20Britain%20have%20responded%20with%20two%20rounds%20of%20joint%20strikes%20against%20the%20Huthis%2C%20while%20American%20forces%20have%20also%20carried%20out%20unilateral%20air%20raids%20against%20the%20rebels%2C%20who%20have%20also%20declared%20American%20and%20British%20interests%20to%20be%20legitimate%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20growing%20violence%20in%20multiple%20parts%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20has%20raised%20fears%20of%20a%20broader%20regional%20conflict%20directly%20involving%20Iran%20--%20a%20worst-case%20scenario%20that%20Washington%20is%20desperately%20seeking%20to%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706464440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-06%2Fus-flag-reuters-650_650x400_51466247596.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F3-us-troops-killed-in-drone-attack-in-jordan-amid-israel-hamas-war-4949398%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20drone%20attack%20on%20a%20base%20in%20Jordan%20killed%20three%20American%20troops%20on%20Sunday%2C%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20blaming%20Iran-backed%20militants%20and%20vowing%20to%20hold%20the%20perp