cy%20reserved%20for%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20candidates%20can%20be%20declared%20unreserved%20if%20enough%20candidates%20from%20these%20categories%20are%20not%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'Guidelines%20for%20Implementation%20of%20the%20Reservation%20Policy%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%20Higher%20Education%20Institutes%20(HEIs)'%20are%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20for%20feedback%20from%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20guidelines%20have%20been%20receiving%20backlash%20from%20several%20quarters.%20The%20Congress%20alleged%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B%20to%20end%20reservation%20given%20to%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20OBCs%20in%20posts%20in%20higher%20education%20institutions%20and%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20only%20doing%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20of%20symbolism%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20issues%20of%20Dalits%2C%20backward%20classes%20and%20tribals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JNU%20Students'%20Union%20(JNUSU)%20also%20staged%20a%20protest%20against%20it%20and%20burnt%20an%20effigy%20of%20UGC%20Chairman%20M%20Jagadesh%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20also%20clarified%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20de-reservation%20of%20reserved%20category%20positions%20in%20Central%20Educational%20Institutions%20(CEI)%20in%20the%20past%20and%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20no%20such%20de-reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReservation%20in%20Central%20Educational%20Institutions%20is%20provided%20for%20all%20posts%20in%20direct%20recruitment%20in%20Teacher's%20cadre%20as%20per%20the%20Central%20Educational%20Institutions%20(Reservation%20in%20Teachers'%20Cadre)%20Act%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20enactment%20of%20this%20Act%2C%20no%20reserved%20post%20is%20to%20be%20de-reserved.%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20has%20given%20directives%20to%20all%20the%20CEIs%20to%20fill%20up%20the%20vacancies%20strictly%20as%20per%20the%202019%20ACT%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20wrote%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC%20chairman%20also%20posted%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20to%20clarify%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20de-reservation%20of%20reserved%20category%20positions%20in%20Central%20Educational%20Institutions%20in%20the%20past%20and%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20no%20such%20de-reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20for%20all%20HEIs%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20backlog%20positions%20in%20the%20reserved%20category%20are%20filled%20up%20through%20concerted%20efforts.%26quot%3B%20According%20to%20new%20draft%20guidelines%20by%20the%20UGC%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20vacancy%20reserved%20for%20SC%20or%20ST%20or%20OBC%20cannot%20be%20filled%20by%20a%20candidate%20other%20than%20an%20SC%20or%20ST%20or%20OBC%20candidate%2C%20as%20the%20case%20may%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20a%20reserved%20vacancy%20may%20be%20declared%20unreserved%20by%20following%20the%20procedure%20of%20de-reservation%20where%20after%2C%20it%20can%20be%20filled%20as%20an%20unreserved%20vacancy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20general%20ban%20on%20de-reservation%20of%20reserved%20vacancies%20in%20case%20of%20direct%20recruitment.%20However%2C%20in%20rare%20and%20exceptional%20cases%20when%20a%20vacancy%20in%20a%20Group%20A%20service%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20remain%20vacant%20in%20public%20interest%2C%20the%20University%20concerned%20may%20prepare%20a%20proposal%20for%20de-reservation%20of%20the%20vacancy%20giving%20the%20following%20information%3A%20The%20proposal%20will%20be%20required%20to%20list%20--%20efforts%20made%20to%20fill%20up%20the%20post%3B%20reasons%20why%20it%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20remain%20vacant%20and%20justification%20for%20de-reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20proposal%20for%20de-reservation%20in%20case%20of%20Group%20C%20or%20D%20should%20go%20to%20the%20Executive%20Council%20of%20the%20University%20and%20in%20case%20of%20Group%20A%20or%20B%20should%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20giving%20full%20details%2C%20for%20necessary%20approval.%20After%20receiving%20the%20approval%2C%20the%20post%20may%20be%20filled%20and%20reservation%20may%20be%20carried%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20draft%20guidelines%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20promotion%2C%20if%20sufficient%20numbers%20of%20SC%20and%20ST%20candidates%20fit%20for%20promotion%20against%20reserved%20vacancies%20are%20not%20available%2C%20such%20vacancies%20may%20be%20de-reserved%20and%20filled%20by%20the%20candidates%20of%20other%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20power%20to%20accord%20approval%20to%20the%20de-reservation%20of%20the%20reserved%20vacancies%20in%20such%20cases%20will%20be%20delegated%20to%20UGC%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20if%20certain%20conditions%20are%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20proposal%20can%20be%20considered%20if%20no%20candidate%20belonging%20to%20the%20category%20for%20which%20the%20vacancy%20is%20reserved%20is%20available%20within%20the%20zone%20of%20consideration%20or%20extended%20zone%20of%20consideration%20or%20eligible%20for%20promotion%20in%20the%20feeder%20cadre%20specified%20in%20the%20recruitment%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20approval%20for%20de-reservation%20has%20been%20seen%20and%20concurred%20in%20by%20the%20liaison%20officer%20for%20SCST%20of%20the%20university.%20The%20proposal%20for%20de-reservation%20is%20agreed%20by%20the%20appropriate%20authority%20in%20UGC%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20case%20of%20disagreement%20between%20the%20appointing%20authority%20and%20the%20liaison%20officer%20for%20SC%2C%20ST%20of%20the%20university%2C%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20is%20obtained%20and%20implemented%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20guidelines%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20