0this%20has%20revived%20Mr%20Kumar's%20earlier%20reputation%20as%20%26quot%3BPaltu%20Ram%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20has%20amassed%20a%20handful%20of%20pejoratives%20%E2%80%93%20from%20%26quot%3BTired%26quot%3Bto%20%26quot%3Bchameleon%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20was%20the%20second%20time%20Mr%20Kumar%20had%20dumped%20the%20Opposition%20and%20sought%20greener%20fields%20under%20the%20NDA%20banner.%20The%20last%20time%20he%20did%20so%20was%20in%202017%2C%20when%20he%20refused%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20Grand%20Alliance%20after%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20Lalu%20Yadav%20and%20his%20son%20and%20then%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20got%20together%20in%202022%20as%20Mr%20Kumar%20ditched%20the%20BJP%20and%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20RJD%2C%20DMK%2C%20JMM%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20CPI(ML)-L%20and%20AAP%20attacked%20Mr%20Kumar%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20who%20had%20got%20back%20his%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20after%20Nitish%20Kumar%20came%20back%2C%20was%20bitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20a%20tired%20Chief%20Minister...%20I%20can%20give%20you%20in%20writing%20that%20the%20JDU%20party%20will%20be%20finished%20in%202024.%20The%20public%20is%20with%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20called%20Mr%20Kumar%20a%20%26quot%3Bchameleon%26quot%3B.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20the%20party's%20media%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNitish%20Kumar%2C%20who%20frequently%20changes%20political%20partners%2C%20is%20giving%20a%20tough%20competition%20to%20chameleons%20in%20changing%20colours.%26quot%3B%20The%20people%20of%20Bihar%20will%20not%20forgive%20this%20%26quot%3Bexpert%20of%20betrayal%26quot%3B%20and%20those%20who%20are%20making%20him%20dance%20to%20their%20tunes%2C%20he%20added.