.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fone-nation-one-election-an-undemocratic-idea-against-basic-structure-of-constitution-kharge-to-kovind-panel-9117337%2F%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20sake%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Crobust%20democracy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetail.aspx%3FPRID%3D2000148%5C%22%3Efourth%20meeting%20of%20the%20high-level%20committee%20was%20also%20held%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%20(January%2027).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20representative%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20this%20committee%2C%20with%20Congress%20leader%20and%20MP%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20having%20refused%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20Kovind%20said%20that%20polls%20being%20held%20concurrently%20at%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20levels%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fone-nation-one-election-in-national-interest-nothing-to-do-with-any-party-ram-nath-kovind%2Farticle67557721.ece%5C%22%3Eis%20in%20the%20national%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20it%20would%20benefit%20whichever%20party%20was%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbe%20it%20BJP%20or%20Congress%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20November%2021%2C%202023%2C%20Chowdhury%20had%20called%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cparty%20agenda%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20requesting%20all%20the%20political%20parties%20to%20cooperate%20as%20this%20is%20in%20the%20national%20interest.%20No%20political%20party%20has%20got%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kovind%20told%20the%20media%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20a%20public%20notice%2C%20the%20high-level%20committee%20had%20called%20for%20suggestions%2C%20and%20said%20those%20received%20by%20January%2015%20would%20be%20taken%20up%20for%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20leader%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%2C%20who%20is%20also%20former%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3B%20N.K.%20Singh%2C%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%3B%20Subhash%20C.%20Kashyap%2C%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretary%20general%3B%20Sanjay%20Kothari%2C%20former%20chief%20vigilance%20commissioner%20and%20Harish%20Salve%2C%20senior%20advocate%20attended%20the%20meeting%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20government%20release%20on%20the%20meeting%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20presentation%20was%20made%20before%20the%20committee%20based%20on%20the%20research%20paper%20%E2%80%98Macroeconomic%20Impact%20of%20Harmonizing%20Electoral%20Cycles%2C%20Evidences%20from%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20co-authored%20by%20N.K%20Singh%20and%20Prachi%20Mishra.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20also%20decided%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20conversation%20process%20with%20stakeholders%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20argument%20of%20%E2%80%98cost-saving%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20critiqued%20by%20the%20Congress%20already%20when%20Kharge%20wrote%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20committee%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ECI%20had%20estimated%20the%20cost%20of%20conducting%20the%202014%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20VVPAT%20machines%20to%20be%20about%20Rs%203%2C870%20crore%20%E2%80%A6%20The%20argument%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20conducting%20elections%20is%20extremely%20high%20seems%20baseless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20elections%20are%20held%20once%20in%20five%20years%2C%20the%20expenses%20make%20up%20less%20than%200.02%25%20of%20the%20total%20Union%20budget%20for%20the%20preceding%20five%20years.%20When%20elections%20are%20held%20separately%20to%20the%20state%20assemblies%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20election%20is%20fully%20borne%20by%20the%20respective%20states.%20The%20expenses%20for%20assembly%20elections%20may%20also%20be%20a%20similar%20percentage%20of%20their%20state%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20feel%20the%20people%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20consider%20this%20small%20amount%20as%20the%20cost%20of%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20to%20uphold%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI(M)%20has%20also%20written%20to%20the%20committee%20registering%20its%20%E2%80%9Cstrong%20objection%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98ONOE%E2%80%99%20is%20being%20%E2%80%9Csought%20to%20be%20imposed%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20consideration%20of%20the%20proposal%20itself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fcpim-calls-one-nation-one-election-inherently-anti-democratic-in-letter-to-kovind-led-panel-2839525%5C%22%3Eruns%20against%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fgovt-committee-simultaneous-elections-explained-8918921%2F%5C%22%3Ein%202015%2C%20a%20parliamentary%20committee%3C%2Fa%3E%20compiled%20a%20report%20on%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20at%20the%20time%20told%20the%20committee%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cimpractical%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunworkable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20Congress%20called%20the%20report%20anti-democratic%20and%20unconstitutional%2C%20while%20the%20CPI%20and%20the%20NCP%20said%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20feasible%E2%80%9D.%20The%20CPI(M)%20also%20highlighted%20%E2%80%9Cpractical%20problems%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsimultaneous-elections-panel-suggestions-9096160%2F%5C%22%3EKovind-led%20committee%E2%80%99s%20terms%20of%20reference%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20is%20meant%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexamine%20and%20make%20recommendations%20for%20holding%20simultaneous%20elections%20to%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%20(L