of%20humour!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706454480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fpabfp89_tamanna-_625x300_28_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fthis-woman-asked-her-tinder-match-why-should-she-date-him-he-replied-with-a-presentation-4948864%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22X%20user%20Tamanna%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BAsked%20my%20Tinder%20match%20why%20should%20I%20date%20him%20and%20he%20sent%20me%20a%20link%20to%20this%20ppt.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fthis-woman-asked-her-tinder-match-why-should-she-date-him-he-replied-with-a-presentation-4948864%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fthis-woman-asked-her-tinder-match-why-should-she-date-him-he-replied-with-a-presentation-4948864%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fthis-woman-asked-her-tinder-match-why-should-she-date-him-he-replied-with-a-presentation-4948864%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndependent%20Judiciary%20Means...%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice%20As%20Supreme%20Court%20Turns%2075%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%20addressed%20a%20unique%20ceremonial%20bench%20as%20the%20country's%20highest%20court%20turned%2075%20years.%20Similar%20to%20the%20arrangement%20in%201950%20-%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20held%20its%20first%20sitting%20-%20the%20Chief%20Justices%20of%20all%20the%20high%20courts%20also%20attended%20the%20ceremony%20that%20was%20streamed%20live%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20emphasised%20three%20principles%20that%20are%20necessary%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20function%20according%20to%20the%20constitutional%20mandate.%20The%20first%20is%20an%20independent%20judiciary%2C%20where%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20must%20be%20independent%20of%20the%20legislature%20and%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20the%20judicial%20approach%20towards%20adjudication%2C%20which%20says%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20must%20interpret%20the%20Constitution%20not%20as%20a%20rigid%20body%20of%20rules%2C%20but%20as%20a%20living%20organism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20principle%20is%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20must%20secure%20the%20respect%20of%20citizens%20for%20it%20to%20establish%20itself%20as%20a%20legitimate%20institution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20confidence%20of%20citizens%20is%20determinative%20of%20our%20own%20legitimacy...%20This%20court%20has%20in%20the%20last%2075%20years%20faced%20old%20and%20new%20challenges%20in%20confronting%20the%20face%20of%20injustice%20and%20meeting%20the%20expectations%20of%20those%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20entrenches%20several%20institutional%20safeguards%20for%20an%20independent%20judiciary...%20However%2C%20these%20constitutional%20safeguards%20are%20not%20in%20themselves%20sufficient%20to%20ensure%20an%20independent%20judiciary.%20An%20independent%20judiciary%20does%20not%20merely%20mean%20the%20insulation%20of%20the%20institution%20from%20the%20executive%20and%20the%20legislature%20branches%2C%20but%20also%20the%20independence%20of%20individual%20judges%20in%20the%20performance%20of%20their%20roles%20as%20judges%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20art%20of%20judging%20must%20be%20free%20of%20social%20and%20political%20pressure%2C%20and%20from%20the%20inherent%20biases%20which%20human%20beings%20hold.%20Efforts%20are%20being%20made%20from%20within%20the%20institution%20to%20educate%20and%20sensitise%20judges%20across%20courts%20to%20unlearn%20their%20subconscious%20attitudes%20inculcated%20by%20social%20conditioning%20on%20gender%2C%20disability%2C%20race%2C%20caste%2C%20and%20sexuality%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F8b63mfl_narendra-modi-dy-chandrachud_625x300_28_January_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20ceremonial%20bench%20was%20organised%20for%20the%20first%20time%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20also%20participated%20in%20the%20programme%20before%20the%20ceremonial%20sitting%20began.%20A%20new%20website%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20launched%20as%20part%20of%20the%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20explained%20the%20two%20approaches%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20takes%20to%20enhance%20the%20faith%20in%20its%20justice-delivery%20mechanism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20by%20not%20conferring%20permanence%20upon%20judicial%20decisions%2C%20this%20court%20is%20cognisant%20that%20the%20law%20is%20not%20constant%2C%20but%20is%20ever-evolving.%20The%20space%20for%20disagreement%20is%20always%20open.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20strongest%20jurisprudential%20developments%20of%20this%20court%20have%20undergone%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20litigation%20over%20the%20course%20of%20years%2C%20where%20the%20court%20has%20taken%20divergent%20views%20on%20questions%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20second%20approach...%20has%20been%20to%20increase%20access%20to%20courts%20by%20diluting%20the%20procedural%20rules%20for%20the%20institution%20of%20cases.%20This%20court%20was%20opened%20up%20to%20citizens%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20the%20nation%20irrespective%20of%20their%20social%20and%20economic%20status.%20In%201985%2C%2024%2C716%20letter%20petitions%20were%20received%20in%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20and%20other%20regional%20languages.%20This%20number%20has%20since%20then%20undergone%20an%20exponential%20surge.%20In%202022%2C%20about%201%2C15%2C120%20letter%20petitions%20were%20submitted%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20clearly%20indicating%20that%20the%20common%20person%20believes%20that%20they%20would%20be%20able%20to%20secure%20justice%20in%20these%20halls%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20agreed%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20access%20to%20courts%20does%20not%20necessarily%20translate%20into%20access%20to%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court%20has%20over%20the%20course%20of%20years%20faced%20immense%20difficulty%20in%20keeping%20up%20with%20the%20surge%20in%20the%20institution%20of%20cases.%20Currently%2C%20a%20total%20of%2065%2C915%20registered%20cases%20are%20pending%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Much%20as%20we%20would%20like%20to%20reassure%20ourselves%20that%20the%20mounting%20pile%20represents%20the%20faith%20of%20citizens%20in%20the%20line%2C%20we%20need%20to%20ask%20hard%20questions%20on%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20a%20radical%20change%20in%20the%20approach%20to%20decision-making.%20In%20our%20desire%20to%20ensure%20justice%20in%20each%20individual%20case%2C%20should%20we%20risk%20the%20court%20becoming%20dysfunctional%3F%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20we%20have%20to%20have%20a%20common%20understanding%20of%20how%20we%20argue%20and%20how%20we%20decide%20and%20above%20all%2C%20on%20the%20cases%20which%20we%20select%20for%20decision-making.%20If%20we%20do%20not%20make%20hard%20choices%20and%20take%20difficult%20calls%20to%20resolve%20these%20pressing%20issues%2C%20the%20euphoria%20generated%20from%20the%20past%20may%20well%20be%20short-lived%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20soon%20migrate%20its%20digital%20data%20to%20a%20cloud-based%20infrastructure.%20The%20digital%20Supreme%20Court%20reports%20will%20make%20judgments%20available%20to%20people%20for%20free%20in%20a%20digital%20format.%20All%20519%20volumes%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20reports%20since%201950%2C%20covering%2036%2C308%20cases%2C%20will%20be%20available%20in%20digital%20format%2C%20bookmarked%2C%20user-friendly%20and%20with%20open%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706454180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fhuavb7b8_chief-justice-dy-chandrachud_625x300_28_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findependent-judiciary-means-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-as-supreme-court-turns-75-4948855%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%20addressed%20a%20unique%20ceremonial%20bench%20as%20the%20country's%20highest%20court%20turned%2075%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findependent-judiciary-means-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-as-supreme-court-turns-75-4948855%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findependent-judiciary-means-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-as-supreme-court-turns-75-4948855%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findependent-judiciary-means-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-as-supreme-court-turns-75-4948855%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Istanbul%20church%20attack%3A%20Gunmen%20kill%20one%20person%20during%20Sunday%20morning%20mass%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706454103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1430%2Fproduction%2F_132486150_gettyimages-1959485127.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-6