0Ukraine%20shows%20the%20damage%20that%20snipers%20can%20do%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20team%20of%20Green%20Berets%20from%201st%20Special%20Forces%20Group%20(Airborne)%20fire%20at%20long%20range%20targets%20during%20the%20Menton%202022%20Best%20Sniper%20Competition%20at%20Joint%20Base%20Lewis-McChord%2C%20Wash.%2C%20Dec.%208%2C%202022%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b3f5a343bb77284ba0d9f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20team%20of%20Green%20Berets%20from%201st%20Special%20Forces%20Group%20(Airborne)%20fire%20at%20long%20range%20targets%20during%20the%20Menton%202022%20Best%20Sniper%20Competition%20at%20Joint%20Base%20Lewis-McChord%2C%20Wash.%2C%20Dec.%208%2C%202022%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Army%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20Thoman%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESnipers%20are%20valuable%20force%20multipliers%20within%20small%20special%20operations%20teams.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESOCOM%20is%20looking%20for%20an%20new%20extreme%20long-range%20sniper%20rifle%20for%20future%20conflict.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20highlighted%20the%20value%20of%20snipers%20in%20high-intensity%20warfare.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsk%20any%20soldier%2C%20and%20they'll%20tell%20you%20that%20there%20are%20fewer%20scarier%20things%20on%20a%20battlefield%20than%20an%20enemy%20sniper.%20The%20combination%20of%20the%20unknown%20with%20the%20actual%20danger%20elevates%20snipers%20to%20some%20of%20the%20most%20hated%20figures%20in%20warfare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20snipers%20are%20force%20multipliers%2C%20more%20so%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20special%20operations.%20Army%20Rangers%2C%20Navy%20SEALs%2C%20Marine%20Raiders%2C%20and%20Green%20Berets%20fight%20in%20small%20numbers%2C%20and%20the%20snipers%20within%20their%20ranks%20play%20a%20key%20role.%20In%20a%20team%20of%2012-16%20commandos%2C%20many%20will%20be%20sniper-qualified%2C%20thus%20maximizing%20the%20firepower%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20special%20operations%20forces%20are%20now%20looking%20for%20a%20new%2C%20extreme%20long-range%20rifle%20for%20their%20next%20big%20fight%2C%20a%20possible%20high-intensity%20conflict%2C%20as%20t%3C%2Fspan%3Ehe%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20shown%20the%20damage%20that%20snipers%20can%20do%2C%20the%20impact%20they%20can%20have%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20New%20Sniper%20Rifle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20December%2C%20US%20Special%20Operations%20Command%2C%20or%20SOCOM%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsam.gov%2Fopp%2F66418ecd71f5498ba4544d889459a6b2%2Fview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3Ereleased%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20solicitation%20for%20offers%20for%20a%20new%20sniper%20rifle.%20The%20notice%20requires%20certain%20standard%20characteristics%20for%20the%20new%20sniper%20rifle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Extreme%20Long%20Range-Sniper%20Rifle%20(ELR-SR)%20program%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20modular%2C%20magazine-fed%2C%20multi-caliber%20capable%20system%20to%20replace%20the%20M107%20Barret%20and%20MK15%20anti-personnel%20and%20anti-materiel%20sniper%20rifles.%20There%20is%20a%20requirement%20that%20the%20weapon's%20operator%20be%20able%20to%20swap%20barrels%20easily%20within%205%20minutes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESOCOM%20also%20wants%20its%20new%20sniper%20rifle%20to%20be%20significantly%20lighter%20than%20the%20ones%20it%20will%20be%20replacing.%20With%20a%20maximum%20weight%20of%2022%20lbs%2C%20the%20ELR-SR%20will%20be%20almost%209%20lbs%20lighter%20than%20the%20M107%20Barret%20and%20about%205%20lbs%20lighter%20than%20the%20MK15.%20In%20terms%20of%20range%2C%20the%20ELR-SR%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20similar%20to%20older%20sniper%20rifles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221401%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20MK-22%20Precision%20Sniper%20Rifle%20sights%20view%20a%20target%20on%20the%20range%20at%20Joint%20Base%20McGuire-Dix-Lakehurst%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20Oct.%2022%2C%202023.%20The%20MK-22%20replaced%20the%20Army's%20existing%20M2010%20and%20M107%20sniper%20rifles.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b3f8baf4b446f3be9d573a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22926%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20MK-22%20Precision%20Sniper%20Rifle%20sights%20view%20a%20target%20on%20the%20range%20at%20Joint%20Base%20McGuire-Dix-Lakehurst%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20Oct.%2022%2C%202023.%20The%20MK-22%20replaced%20the%20Army's%20existing%20M2010%20and%20M107%20sniper%20rifles.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Army%20National%20Guard%20photo%20by%20Spc.%20Michael%20Schwenk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpecial%20Operations%20Command%20is%20looking%20for%20a%20precision%20weapon%20that%20can%20hit%20targets%20up%20to%202%2C500%20meters%20(1.5%20miles)%20away.%20As%20for%20its%20durability%2C%20SOCOM%20wants%20the%20new%20sniper%20rifle%20to%20have%20a%20barrel%20life%20of%20between%201%2C200%20and%201%2C500%20rounds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20new%20rifle%20should%20be%20capable%20of%20firing%20the%20.300%20Norma%20Mangum%20bullet%2C%20which%20has%20been%20approved%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%2C%20as%20well%20as%20subsonic%20and%20supersonic%20rounds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESOCOM%20also%20specified%20that%20the%20new%20sniper%20rifle%20should%20be%20able%20to%20take%20a%20sound%20suppressor%20no%20more%20than%208.5%20inches%20long%20with%20recoil-reducing%20attributes.%20The%20command%20is%20also%20looking%20for%20a%20rifle%20with%20as%20little%20recoil%20as%20possible%20because%20the%20less%20recoil%20a%20weapon%20has%2C%20the%20more%20accurate%20the%20shooter%20can%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E