%20support%20Taylor%2C%20and%20women%20everywhere%20who%20are%20the%20victims%20of%20this%20kind%20of%20theft%20of%20their%20privacy%20and%20right%20to%20autonomy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20after%20SAG-AFTRA%20members'%20headline-grabbing%20strike%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226122%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20supporters%20of%20SAG-AFTRA%20picket%20holding%20a%20sign%20relating%20to%20the%20union's%20AI%20concerns.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b65180ac2de4f17ee523c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224083%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20supporter%20of%20SAG-AFTRA%20picket%20holding%20a%20sign%20relating%20to%20the%20union's%20AI%20concerns.%3Cp%3EJay%20L.%20Clendenin%20%2F%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20roughly%20160%2C000%20member%20union%20walked%20out%20over%20a%20dispute%20with%20the%20Alliance%20of%20Motion%20Picture%20and%20Television%20Producers%20(AMPTP).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20lasted%20nearly%20four%20months%20before%20a%20deal%20was%20reached%20that%20saw%20members%20win%20pay%20increases%2C%20streaming%20bonuses%2C%20and%20AI%20protections%2C%20which%20gave%20performers%20a%20degree%20of%20control%20over%20the%20use%20of%20digital%20images%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20looking%20to%20reproduce%20actors'%20likenesses%20with%20AI%20must%20now%20first%20obtain%20their%20consent%2C%20and%20the%20stars%20must%20be%20paid%20for%20the%20number%20of%20days%20they%20would%20have%20worked%20to%20perform%20any%20scenes%20featuring%20their%20digital%20replicas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20actors%20are%20still%20concerned%20over%20the%20new%20AI%20terms%2C%20particularly%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bvague%26quot%3B%20consent%20exemptions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2Farticle%2Fsag-aftra-ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMashable%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployers%20are%20not%20required%20to%20gain%20consent%20for%20adjusting%20certain%20performance%20parts%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Blip%20and%2For%20other%20facial%20or%20body%20movement%20and%2For%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20performer%20to%20a%20foreign%20language.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20digital%20replica%20is%20used%20without%20consent%2C%20the%20contract%20also%20fails%20to%20stipulate%20that%20studios%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20change%20their%20footage%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20key%20worries%20include%20the%20use%20of%20%26quot%3Bsynthetic%20performers%26quot%3B%20taking%20over%20from%20real%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20serious%20issue%20of%20them%20all%20is%20the%20inclusion%20in%20the%20agreement%20of%20%26quot%3BSynthetic%20Performers%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BAI%20Objects%2C%26quot%3B%20resembling%20humans.%20This%20gives%20the%20studios%2Fstreamers%20a%20green-light%20to%20use%20human-looking%20AI%20Objects%20instead%20of%20hiring%20a%20human%20actor%2C%26quot%3B%20filmmaker%20Justine%20Bateman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJustineBateman%2Fstatus%2F1723507846678213100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20me%2C%20this%20inclusion%20is%20an%20anathema%20to%20a%20union%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsag-aftra-artificial-intelligence-taylor-swift-photos-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706453247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b64fb26c8f0a134f7a6fc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsag-aftra-artificial-intelligence-taylor-swift-photos-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20actors'%20union%20condemned%20the%20deepfake%20images%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Bupsetting%2C%20harmful%2C%20and%