w%20the%20attacker%2C%20three%20teams%20were%20formed%20to%20first%20identify%20and%20then%20track%20and%20catch%20the%20attacker%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20girl%20had%20no%20reported%20history%20of%20personal%20animosity%2C%20spurned%20advances%2C%20or%20any%20romantic%20involvement%20with%20any%20boy%2C%20making%20the%20incident%20appear%20like%20a%20blind%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20there%20were%20also%20no%20surveillance%20cameras%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20crime%2C%20which%20made%20the%20investigation%20not%20an%20easy%20task%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(north)%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Meena%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20one%20team%20focused%20on%20profiling%20the%20girl%20who%20was%20attacked%2C%20examining%20her%20social%20media%20history%2C%20past%20contacts%2C%20and%20other%20relevant%20details%2C%20another%20was%20tasked%20with%20reviewing%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20six%20roads%20leading%20to%20the%20crime%20scene%2C%20Mr%20Meena%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20team%20positioned%20itself%20near%20schools%20in%20plainclothes%20with%20a%20rough%20description%20of%20the%20attacker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20scrutiny%2C%20the%20CCTV%20team%20identified%20a%20boy%20running%20away%20from%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20crime%20about%20ten%20minutes%20apart%2C%20roughly%20a%20kilometre%20away.%20His%20face%20was%20not%20visible%2C%20but%20the%20boy%20matched%20the%20description%20provided%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20DCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20resorted%20to%20playing%20back%20the%20video%20in%20slow%20motion%20and%20eventually%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20more%20accurate%20description%2C%20based%20on%20which%20the%20suspect%20was%20caught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20confessed%20to%20the%20crime%20during%20interrogation%2C%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvidence%2C%20including%20the%20caustic%