22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcongress-vs-regional-parties-in-india-bloc-nitish-kumar-becomes-first-leader-to-walk-out-of-opposition-alliance%2Farticleshow%2F107206662.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Alliance%2C%20Same%20Nitish%20Kumar%20-%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister's%20Record%209th%20Oath%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENitish%20Kumar%20took%20oath%20today%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%20for%20a%20record%20ninth%20time%2C%20at%20the%20head%20of%20a%20fresh%20government%20formed%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20BJP.%20Mr%20Kumar%20is%20replacing%20his%20ministers%20from%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20with%20those%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20party%20leaders%20Samrat%20Chowdhury%2C%20Vijay%20Sinha%20and%20several%20others%20also%20took%20oath%20along%20with%20him%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20this%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20congratulated%20the%20new%20governmnet%20with%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NDA%20government%20formed%20in%20Bihar%20will%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20state%20and%20to%20fulfill%20the%20aspirations%20of%20its%20people.%20I%20congratulate%20%40NitishKumar.%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Samrat%20Chaudhary%20ji%20and%20Vijay%20Sinha%20ji%20on%20taking%20oath%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20this%20team%20will%20serve%20my%20family%20members%20of%20the%20state%20with%20full%20dedication%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20rough%20translation%20of%20his%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20the%20fifth%20time%20in%20a%20decade%20the%2072-year-old%20has%20changed%20camp%20--%20the%20frequency%20of%20the%20process%20having%20earned%20him%20the%20pejorative%20%26quot%3BPaltu%20Kumar%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20had%20parted%20company%20with%20the%20BJP%20last%20in%202022.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20concerned%20that%20the%20BJP%20could%20engineer%20a%20split%20in%20his%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20as%20they%20did%20in%20Maharashtra%20with%20the%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20joining%20the%20NDA%20fold%20again%20today%2C%20he%20cited%20his%20disappointment%20with%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20saying%20though%20he%20got%20the%20front%20up%20and%20running%2C%20very%20little%20was%20being%20done%20by%20the%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20new%20Grand%20Alliance%20that%20we%20created%20(in%20August%202022)%20is%20not%20in%20a%20good%20condition.%20The%20situation%20is%20not%20looking%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20working%20hard%20to%20make%20a%20successful%2C%20meaningful%20(INDIA)%20alliance%2C%20but%20no%20one%20else%20(in%20the%20alliance)%20has%20been%20doing%20anything...%20Gathbandhan%20main%20bhi%20gadbad%20chal%20rahan%20hai%20(something%20is%20wrong%20in%20the%20alliance).%20People%20are%20not%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%2C%20though%2C%C2%A0%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%20has%20been%20upset%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20in%20INDIA%20bloc's%20poll%20preparations%20and%20being%20passed%20over%20as%20a%20possible%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate.%20The%20delays%20to%20seat-sharing%20talks%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20had%20been%20a%20further%20aggravation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706448420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ft0v8geo8_niths-kumar-oath-1200_625x300_28_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-takes-oath-as-bihar-chief-minister-for-record-9th-time-4947828%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20took%20oath%20today%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%20for%20a%20record%20ninth%20time%2C%20at%20the%20head%20of%20a%20govern