mg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29095001%2FScreenshot-2023-11-29-at-9.49.41-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20has%20come%20up%20with%20draft%20rules%20to%20de-reserve%20the%20posts%20of%20faculty%20members%20in%20higher%20education%20institutions%20if%20%E2%80%98enough%20reserved%20candidates%20are%20not%20available%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fthesundaystandard%2F2024%2FJan%2F28%2Fdraft-ugc-guidelines-seek-to-open-de-reservation-window%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20guidelines%20were%20released%20in%20the%20last%20week%20of%20December.%20They%20are%20open%20for%20public%20opinion%20till%20today.%20The%20posts%20in%20question%20are%20meant%20for%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20these%20posts%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20de-reserved%20for%20unreserved%20category%20candidates.%20But%20for%20Group%20A%20posts%2C%20a%20university%20can%20prepare%20a%20proposal%20for%20de-reservation%20as%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20allowed%20to%20remain%20vacant%20in%20%E2%80%98public%20interest%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20the%20draft%20guidelines%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20do%20so%2C%20it%20would%20have%20to%20provide%20information%20like%20the%20designation%2C%20pay%20scale%2C%20name%20of%20the%20service%2C%20responsibilities%2C%20required%20qualifications%2C%20efforts%20made%20to%20fill%20the%20post%2C%20and%20why%20it%20cannot%20be%20allowed%20to%20remain%20vacant%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Group%20C%20and%20D%20posts%20can%20be%20de-reserved%20by%20the%20executive%20council%20of%20the%20university%20itself%20while%20for%20Group%20A%20posts%2C%20the%20proposal%20has%20to%20be%20submitted%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guidelines%20would%20apply%20to%20all%20the%20central%20universities%2C%20deemed-to-be-universities%2C%20and%20other%20autonomous%20bodies%2Finstitutions%20under%20the%20central%20government%20or%20those%20receiving%20grant-in-aid%20from%20the%20UGC%2C%20central%20government%2C%20or%20consolidated%20fund%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20rules%20would%20apply%20in%20promotion%20policies%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20rules%20argued%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20shortfall%20in%20reserved%20category%20posts%20and%20the%20institutions%20should%20fill%20the%20vacant%20posts%20by%20starting%20a%20recruitment%20drive%20for%20the%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706435942000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29095001%2FScreenshot-2023-11-29-at-9.49.41-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fdraft-ugc-guidelines-suggest-de-reserving-faculty-positions-in-universities%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20rules%20would%20apply%20in%20promotion%20policies%2C%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fdraft-ugc-guidelines-suggest-de-reserving-faculty-positions-in-universities%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20resigns%2C%20stakes%20claim%20to%20form%20govt%20in%20Bihar%20with%20BJP's%20support%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706435804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F26%2Ffull%2F1703608997-4544.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fnitish-kumar-resigns-says-things-did-not-work-well-for-him-in-alliances-124012800167_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20have%20submitted%20my%20resignation%20to%20the%20Governor.%20The%20government%20that%20was%20in%2