0governor%20has%20accepted%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leader%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20PTI%20reported%2C%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20continue%20as%20the%20caretaker%20chief%20minister%20until%20the%20new%20government%20is%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20his%20resignation%2C%20Nitish%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20working%20on%20an%20alliance%20(INDIA)%20for%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%20but%20things%20were%20not%20working%20out.%20Now%2C%20we%20will%20form%20a%20new%20alliance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Patna%20%7C%20Bihar%20outgoing%20CM%20and%20JD(U)%20president%20Nitish%20Kumar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20have%20resigned%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20I%20have%20also%20told%20the%20Governor%20to%20dissolve%20the%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20This%20situation%20came%20because%20not%20everything%20was%20alright%E2%80%A6I%20was%20getting%20views%20from%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwOVGFJSKKH%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FwOVGFJSKKH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1751485594902130748%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20situation%20came%20because%20not%20everything%20was%20alright%E2%80%A6I%20was%20getting%20views%20from%20everyone.%20I%20listened%20to%20all%20of%20them.%20Today%2C%20the%20government%20has%20been%20dissolved%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20resignation%2C%20the%20decision%20was%20reportedly%20taken%20that%20Bihar%20will%20now%20have%20two%20new%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20%E2%80%93%20Vijay%20Sinha%20and%20Samrat%20Choudhary%2C%20both%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20RJD%20is%20currently%20the%20single-largest%20party%20in%20the%20243-member%20Bihar%20Assembly%2C%20with%2079%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20but%20is%20far%20behind%20the%20halfway%20mark%20(122)%20on%20its%20own.%20The%20BJP%20is%20the%20second-largest%20party%2C%20with%2078%20MLAs%2C%20and%20the%20JD(U)%20has%2045%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20past%20week%20had%20been%20rife%20with%20speculation%20about%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20move.%20The%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20is%20famous%20for%20his%20regular%20shifts%20between%20alliances%2C%20irrespective%20of%20ideology.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fayaram-gayaram-politics-of-nitish-at-play-poised-to-rejoin-nda%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nitish%20has%20a%20habit%20of%20being%20fickle%20towards%20his%20allies.%20In%202017%2C%20the%20RJD%20was%20in%20the%20dark%20when%20Nitish%20suddenly%20announced%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20Mahagathbandhan.%20Then%2C%20when%20he%20left%20the%20BJP%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20too%20had%20no%20clue%2C%20until%20he%20announced%20his%20decision%20to%20again%20switch%20camps.%20Reports%20now%20suggest%20that%20even%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20with%20whom%20Nitish%20goes%20back%20a%20long%20time%20both%20as%20friend%20and%20foe%2C%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20aware%20of%20any%20new%20move%20by%20Nitish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20alliance%20leaders%20have%20criticised%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20move.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20Ram%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20Paltu%20Ram%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20BJP%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20himself%20had%20called%20Nitish%20Paltu%20Ram%20when%20he%20had%20joined%20hands%20with%20Lalu.%20Shah%20had%20said%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20doors%20are%20closed%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar.%20Now%20what%20happened%20to%20that%3F%20The%20BJP%20people%20are%20the%20b