01%2F28113617%2FGE4er87XgAAfTop.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ENine%20Western%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Australia%2C%20Canada%2C%20Italy%2C%20Germany%2C%20Finland%2C%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20Switzerland%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20%E2%80%93%20have%20stopped%20their%20funding%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20Refugees%20in%20the%20Near%20East%20(UNRWA).%20This%20move%20comes%20soon%20after%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ficj-says-israel-must-comply-with-genocide-convention-but-stops-short-of-halting-military-operation%5C%22%3Eruling%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20said%20Israel%20must%20comply%20with%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20in%20its%20actions%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNRWA%20had%20earlier%20opened%20an%20investigation%20after%20Israel%20alleged%20that%20some%20of%20its%20employees%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20by%20Hamas.%20Israel%20had%20asked%20all%20countries%20to%20stop%20funding%20the%20agency%20because%20of%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalestinian%20authorities%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F1%2F27%2Fpalestinians-slam-suspension-of-unrwa-funding-by-some-western-nations%5C%22%3Espoken%20out%20strongly%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20aid%20funding%20at%20this%20crucial%20time.%20Two%20Western%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20Ireland%20and%20Norway%20%E2%80%93%20have%20so%20far%20publicly%20stated%20that%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20fund%20UNRWA%20as%20the%20agency%20provides%20critical%20help%20to%20Palestinian%20refugees%20and%20those%20displaced%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20UNRWA%20commissioner%20general%20Philippe%20Lazzarini%20has%20said%20this%20funding%20suspension%20is%20%E2%80%9Cshocking%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20lives%20of%20people%20in%20Gaza%20depends%20on%20this%20support%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20UNRWA%20had%20already%20taken%20action%20against%20the%20employees%20Israel%20had%20raised%20questions%20over%20and%20begun%20an%20impartial%20investigation.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20immensely%20irresponsible%20to%20sanction%20an%20Agency%20and%20an%20entire%20community%20it%20serves%20because%20of%20allegations%20of%20criminal%20acts%20against%20some%20individuals%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20of%20war%2C%20displacement%20and%20political%20crises%20in%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20Lazzarini%E2%80%99s%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNine%20countries%20have%20as%20of%20today%20temporarily%20suspended%20their%20funding%20to%20UNRWA.%20These%20decisions%20threaten%20our%20ongoing%20humanitarian%20work%20across%20the%20region%20including%20and%20especially%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20shocking%20to%20see%20a%20suspension%20of%20funds%20to%20the%20Agency%20in%20reaction%20to%20allegations%20against%20a%20small%20group%20of%20staff%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20immediate%20action%20that%20UNRWA%20took%20by%20terminating%20their%20contracts%20and%20asking%20for%20a%20transparent%20independent%20investigation.%E2%80%AFThe%20United%20Nations%20Office%20of%20Internal%20Oversight%20Services%20(OIOS)%2C%20the%20highest%20investigative%20authority%20in%20the%20UN%20system%2C%20has%20already%20been%20seized%20of%20this%20very%20serious%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUNRWA%20is%20the%20primary%20humanitarian%20agency%20in%20Gaza%2C%20with%20over%202%20million%20people%20depending%20on%20it%20for%20their%20sheer%20survival.%E2%80%AF%E2%80%AF%20Many%20are%20hungry%20as%20the%20clock%20is%20ticking%20towards%20a%20looming%20famine.%20The%20Agency%20runs%20shelters%20for%20over%201%20million%20people%20and%20provides%20food%20and%20primary%20healthcare%20even%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20hostilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20its%20ruling%20yesterday%2C%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20ordered%20that%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIsrael%20must%20take%20immediate%20and%20effective%20measures%20to%20enable%20the%20provision%20of%20urgently%20needed%20basic%20services%20and%20humanitarian%20assistance%20to%20address%20the%20adverse%20conditions%20of%20life%20faced%20by%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%E2%80%AFThese%20measures%20are%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20irreparable%20damage%20to%20the%20rights%20of%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20way%20that%20this%20can%20be%20done%20is%20through%20cooperation%20with%20international%20partners%2C%20especially%20UNRWA%20as%20the%20largest%20humanitarian%20actor%20in%20Gaza.%20Some%203%2C000%20core%20staff%20out%20of%2013%2C000%20in%20Gaza%20continue%20to%20report%20to%20work%2C%20giving%20their%20communities%20a%20lifeline%20which%20can%20collapse%20anytime%20now%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20immensely%20irresponsible%20to%20sanction%20an%20Agency%20and%20an%20entire%20community%20it%20serves%20because%20of%20allegations%20of%20criminal%20acts%20against%20some%20individuals%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20of%20war%2C%20displacement%20and%20political%20crises%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUNRWA%20shares%20the%20list%20of%20all%20its%20staff%20with%20host%20countries%20every%20year%2C%20including%20Israel.%20The%20Agency%20never%20received%20any%20concerns%20on%20specific%20staff%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeanwhile%2C%20an%20investigation%20by%20OIOS%20into%20the%20heinous%20allegations%20will%20establish%20the%20facts.%20Moreover%2C%20as%20I%20announced%20on%2017%20January%2C%20an%20independent%20review%20by%20external%20experts%20will%20help%20UNRWA%20strengthen%20its%20framework%20for%20the%20strict%20adherence%20of%20all%20staff%20to%20the%20humanitarian%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20urge%20countries%20who%20have%20suspended%20their%20funding%20to%20re-consider%20their%20decisions%20before%20UNRWA%20is%20forced%20to%20suspend%20its%20humanitarian%20response.%20The%20lives%20of%20people%20in%20Gaza%20depend%20on%20this%20support%20and%20so%20does%20regional%20stability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706422010000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28113617%2FGE4er87XgAAfTop.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flives-in-gaza-depends-on-this-support-says-unrwa-as-9-western-countries-stop-funding-agency%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20immensely%20irresponsible%20to%20sanction%20an%20Agency%20and%20an%20entire%20community%20it%20serves%20because%20of%20allegations%20of%20criminal%20acts%20against%20some%20individuals%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20of%20war%2C%20displacement%20and%20political%20crises%20in%20the%20region.%E2%80%AF%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Flives-in-gaza-depends-on-this-support-says-unrwa-as-9-western-countries-stop-funding-agency%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Icon%20of%20the%20Seas'%3A%20All%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20world's%20largest%20cruise%20ship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706421481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107199370%2Cimgsize-637331.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Froyal-caribbeans-icon-of-the-seas-worlds-largest-cruise-ship-sets-sail%2Farticleshow%2F107199313.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107199313.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERoyal%2