20Lord%20Ram%20has%20finally%20returned%20to%20Ayodhya%20as%20a%20baby%20(Balak%20Ram)%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20five%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuddenly%20everything%20is%20in%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWasn%E2%80%99t%20Ram%20banished%20by%20his%20own%20father%20for%2014%20years%20to%20a%20forest%20when%20he%20was%20just%20a%20teenager%3F%20If%20so%2C%20how%20can%20he%20be%20said%20to%20have%20%E2%80%98returned%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20baby%3F%20Both%20Valmiki%E2%80%99s%20Ramayana%20and%20Tulsidas%E2%80%99s%20Ram%20Charit%20Manas%20tell%20us%20Ram%20returned%20as%20an%20adult%20and%20ruled%20for%20long%2C%20leaving%20behind%20twin%20sons%20and%20timeless%20memories%20of%20his%20glorious%20rule%3A%20the%20Ram%20Rajya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20284px)%2085vw%2C%20284px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22284%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22346%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20the%20strange%20discovery%20and%20relocation%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20first%20as%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20and%20then%20as%20Balak%20Ram%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20of%20dreams%20regarding%20buried%20treasures%20and%20holy%20relics%20form%20a%20vast%20invisible%20network%20in%20India.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20Ram%2C%20these%20ancient%20tracks%20have%20gotten%20effortlessly%20linked%20with%20each%20other%20through%20folk%20songs%2C%20recitations%20and%20annual%20re-enactments%20of%20the%20epics%20about%20Ram.%20Everyone%2C%20from%20rural%20women%20pounding%20rice%20or%20grinding%20wheat%20to%20wandering%20bands%20of%20Sadhus%20and%20poets%20from%20non-Hindu%20sects%2C%20has%20sung%20the%20tale%20in%20various%20languages.%20One%20such%20Awadhi%20song%20runs%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRam%20suffered%20many%20misfortunes%20walking%20under%20the%20hot%20sun%20with%20his%20loyal%20but%20very%20young%20brother%20and%20a%20beautiful%20wife%20who%20had%20never%20been%20out%20in%20the%20sun.%20Ravana%2C%20who%20abducted%20her%2C%20was%20righly%20burnt%20to%20a%20crisp.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ram%20per%20paral%20bipatiya%20bipatiya%20ho!%3Cbr%3E%5CnLachhiman%20Larikva%2C%20na%20baate%20abodh%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnArey%20Sita%20aisi%20sundar%20rahilin%20ghamva%20maan%20batin%3Cbr%3E%5CnKe%20jari%20gayo%20Ravanaa%20bedardiya%2C%20na%20baaanchyo%E2%80%A6)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdols%20of%20Ram%2C%20Sita%20and%20Lakshman%20are%20periodically%20discovered%20amid%20ruins%2C%20tanks%20or%20rivers%20even%20now.%20Most%20of%20them%20belong%20to%20the%20post%2012th%20century%20when%20images%20of%20Hindu%20gods%20began%20being%20crafted%20for%20temples%20that%20sprouted%20up%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20Vindhyas.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EMaajha%20Pravas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20travelogue%20by%20a%20Marathi%20pilgrim%2C%20Parashuram%20Baba%20the%20ancient%20priest%20of%20a%20temple%20of%20Kale%20Ram%20told%20him%20the%20three%20statues%20of%20Ram%2C%20Lakshmana%20and%20Janaki%20in%20the%20temple%20had%20appeared%20to%20his%20grandfather%20in%20a%20dream%20when%20visiting%20Ayodhya.%20He%20rescued%20them%20from%20the%20Sarayu%20river.%20This%20must%20be%20was%20around%20the%2017th-%2018th%20century.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20a%20generous%20Maratha%20chieftain%2C%20they%20were%20duly%20installed%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20river%20Sarayu.%20Vishnu%20Bhatt%20also%20records%20paying%20an%20entrance%20fee%20of%20Re%201%20and%20four%20annas%20in%201858%2C%20a%20large%20sum%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20is%20that%20temple%2C%20one%20wonders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20in%20post-independence%20India%2C%20an%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20was%20again%20salvaged%20from%20Sarayu%20waters%20by%20a%20sadhu%20after%20he%20dreamt%20of%20it.%20Despite%20objections%20from%20the%20government%2C%20the%20idol%20was%20brought%20out%20and%20installed%20within%20a%20mosque%20as%20Ram%20Lalla.%20Long%20litigation%20followed%20and%20the%20statue%20was%20relocated%20to%20a%20makeshift%20but%20heavily%20protected%20tent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20long%20period%20of%20acrimony%20followed%2C%20until%20in%202019%20the%20NDA%20government%20got%20a%20go-ahead%20signal%20from%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20media%20images%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20dreamlines%20and%20the%20litigation%20and%20the%20blood%20shed.%20On%20January%2022%20morning%2C%20all%20dailies%20flaunted%20large%20poster-size%20front-page%20ads.%20Hyperventilating%20headlines%20heralded%20the%20%E2%80%9Carrival%E2%80%9D%20of%20Ram%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20Ram%20Rajya%20in%20India%20after%20500%20years.%20Large%20photos%20of%20leaders%20and%20priests%20with%20severe%20patriarchal%20faces%20graced%20the%20media%20and%20outdoor%20hoardings.%20Their%20raised%20hands%20signalled%20a%20war%20won%2C%20the%20controlled%20features%20showed%20neither%20anxiety%20nor%20defeat%2C%20but%20an%20unmistakable%20gleam%20of%20fervour%20and%20triumph%20in%20their%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHastily%20scrawled%20notes%20on%20index%20cards%20while%20watching%20the%20event%20on%20TV%20and%20fragments%20of%20Hindi%20dailies%20on%20my%20desk%20are%20chaotic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTapsya%2C%20ascetic%20life%20for%20eleven%20days%20without%20eating%20grains%20and%20sleeping%20on%20the%20hard%20floor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeadership%20says%20%E2%80%9Cchosen%20by%20god%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20grand%20task%20of%20bringing%20him%20home%20after%20500%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJyotishis%20from%20Kashi%20crafted%20the%20time%20chart%20for%20the%20divine%20Abhijit%20Muhurtam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20crosses%2032%20steps%20and%20five%20Mandapams%20carrying%20silver%20articles%20on%20a%20red%20and%20gold%20folded%20cloth%E2%80%9D%2C%20does%20Sashtang%20Pranamam%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20womb%20room%20the%20leaders%20felt%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CSupernatural%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CDivine%E2%80%9Denergies%20flowing%20into%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COvercome%20by%20emotions.%20Have%20no%20word%20to%20describe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBollywood%20actor%20shouting%20Jai%20Shree%20Ram%20then%20looking%20to%20see%20if%20cameras%20had%20caught%20it%2C%20then%20again%20Jai%20Shree%20Ram!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConfirm%20with..evening%20bulletin%20later.%20Check%20X%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%20samaroh%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20more%20of%20a%20victory%20celebration%2C%20like%20a%20Rajasuya%20Yagna.%20The%20cameras%20showed%20a%20few%20solemnly%20performing%20the%20rigid%20rituals.%20Other%20invitees%20watched%20it%20on%20large%20screens%20outside.%20Security%20is%20tight.%20Several%20VIPs%20say%20they%20failed%20to%20get%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommoners%20had%20already%20been%20requested%20to%20stay%20away%20on%20January%2022.%20Now%20Cabinet%20colleagues%20have%20also%20been%20politely%20asked%20to%20postpone%20their%20visits.%20Reason%20being%20crowds%20of%20common%20folks%20from%20all%20over%20are%20overwhelming%20the%20local%20administration.%20One%20learns%20from%20the%20media%20that%20to%20get%20a%20room%20to%20stay%20there%20until%20one%20can%20get%20a%20darshan%20is%20almost%20as%20hard%20as%20getting%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20corridor%20of%20a%20tiny%20hotel%20in%20some%20over%20crowded%20hill%C2%A0%20station%20in%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mega%20star%20from%20Bollywood%20said%20to%20have%20bought%20land%20for%20a%20home%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20is%20seen%20in%20a%20builder%E2%80%99s%20ad%20offering%20cottages%20with%20easy%20EMIs%20in%20Ayodhya.%20There%20are%20other%20unmistakable%20images%20of%20the%20boom%20of%20easy%20money%20and%20dazzling%20transactions%20in%20the%20town%20that%20has%20made%20it%20to%20the%20highest%20category%20in%20the%20religious%20tourism%20circuit.%20The%20local%20shopkeepers%20all%20dressed%20in%20shades%20of%20saffron%20and%20yellow%20are%20euphoric.%20Not%20just%20Lucknow%20but%20the%20newly%20built%20airport%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20they%20tell%20the%20channels%2C%20has%20never%20before%20seen%20so%20many%20private%20jets%20carrying%20VIPs%20from%20all%20spheres%3A%20corporate%2C%20politics%2C%20cricket%2C%20Bollywood%2C%20event%20managers%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20camera%20crews%20then%20move%20on%20to%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade%20and%20the%20honoured%20guest%20from%20France.%20Images%20of%20cordoned-off%20VIP%20areas%20packed%20with%20VIPs%20with%20grim%20faces%20wearing%20shades%2C%20curious%20wives%20eyeing%20each%20other%20slyly.%20The%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20face%20above%20his%20carefully%20clipped%20beard%20looks%20pale%20and%20still.%20Once%20in%20a%20while%20he%20inclines%20his%20head%20slightly%20and%20raises%20his%20thick%20white%20eyebrows%2C%20otherwise%20not%20a%20muscle%20moves%20in%20the%20face.%20A%20man%20of%20immense%2C%20stubborn%2C%20unretreating%2C%20unhesitating%2C%20implacable%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20garden%20of%20centrally%20approved%20patriotism%20blooms%20on%20the%20floats%20from%20states%2C%20on%20what%20was%20Raj%20Path%20(the%20king%E2%80%99s%20avenue)%20and%20is%20now%20Kartavya%20Path%20(Duty%20Avenue).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20nation%20long%20in%20bondage%20of%20colonial%20masters%20degraded%20as%20an%20object%2C%20seeks%20a%20self%20image%2C%20an%20identity%20of%20its%20own.%20Raj%20is%20out%2C%20Kartavya%20is%20in.%20Should%20we%20then%20expect%20on%20any%20Poornima%20or%20Ekadashi%20or%20Amavasya%20or%20Samkranti%2C%20a%20choreographed%20explosion%20of%20veneration%20for%20%E2%80%98our%E2%80%99%20god%2C%20resonating%20in%20remote%20towns%20often%20in%20simultaneous%20acts%20of%20retaliation%20against%20selected%20religious%20symbols%20and%20monuments%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBulldozers%20never%20had%20it%20so%20good.%20The%20cameramen%20have%20never%20used%20the%20long%20shot%20for%20rallies%20so%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalan%20Piya%20(an%2018th%20century%20singer%20poet)%E2%80%99s%20thumri%20in%20Raag%20Kafi%20comes%20to%20mind%3A%20%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20there%20go%20Ram%20and%20his%20younger%20brother%20with%20the%20daughter%20of%20king%20Janak%2FWith%20king%20Dashrath%E2%80%99s%20passing%20Awadh%20has%20lost%20its%20happy%20soul%2F%20Men%20and%20women%20singed%20by%20fires%20of%20sorrow%2FWatch%20the%20queen%20mother%20Kaushalya%20weeping%20all%20by%20herself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaakhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706420947000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28111742%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-26-at-11.45.12-AM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpadharo-mhare-des%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pran%20pratishtha%20samaroh%20was%20more%20of%20a%20victory%20celebration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpadharo-mhare-des%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Saturday%20Night%20Live%E2%80%99%3A%20Jimmy%20Fa