vya%3C%2Fem%3E%20temple%20has%20been%20built%20for%20him%3F%20Could%20Ram%20have%20gone%20away%20because%20his%20temple%20was%20supposedly%20destroyed%20by%20Babar%3F%20Does%20the%20temple%20have%20to%20be%20bhavya%20to%20please%20Ram%20or%20is%20it%20to%20appease%20our%20ego%20that%20we%20can%20build%20on%20a%20grand%20scale%3F%20Would%20Maryada%20Purushottam%20Ram%20approve%20of%20such%20extravaganza%2C%20when%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20Indians%20live%20in%20uncivilised%20conditions%2C%20far%20from%20any%20conception%20of%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Rajya%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20does%20not%20want%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Rajya%E2%80%99%3F%20It%20has%20been%20a%20national%20goal.%20M.K.%20Gandhi%20proposed%20a%20plan%20for%20achieving%20it.%20Rulers%20are%20again%20talking%20about%20attaining%20this%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20is%20attributed%20to%20%E2%80%9Ca%20legal%20battle%20continued%20for%20decades%20over%20the%20existence%20of%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D.%20Actually%2C%20the%20fight%20was%20over%20the%20location%20of%20a%20temple%20and%20not%20people%E2%80%99s%20belief%20in%20Ram.%20If%20he%20is%20an%20incarnation%20of%20Vishnu%2C%20does%20he%20not%20reside%20in%20every%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20and%20therefore%20in%20all%20of%20existence%2C%20including%20every%20human%20being%3F%20So%2C%20does%20the%20destruction%20or%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20temple%20by%20humans%20change%20anything%20regarding%20his%20existence%20and%20abode%3F%20The%20prime%20minister%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cgratitude%20to%20the%20judiciary%20which%20preserved%20the%20dignity%20of%20justice%E2%80%9D.%20Has%20the%20judiciary%20brought%20back%20the%20omnipresent%20Ram%3F%20Further%2C%20if%20he%20is%20in%20all%20of%20us%20and%20pervasive%2C%20why%20did%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Rajya%E2%80%99%20end%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20destruction%20and%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20temple%20not%20a%20human%20act%20for%20a%20political%20purpose%3F%20For%20consolidating%20one%E2%80%99s%20power%20through%20propagating%20one%E2%80%99s%20politics%20using%20religion%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConception%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%2C%20it%20is%20believed%2C%20whether%20as%20avatar%20or%20a%20mortal%20king%2C%20established%20a%20just%20society%20during%20his%20time.%20What%20was%20that%20conception%20of%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Rajya%E2%80%99%3F%20How%20did%20society%20stray%20away%20from%20that%20conception%20in%20the%20land%20where%20he%20has%20been%20revered%3F%20It%20could%20only%20be%20the%20result%20of%20societal%20dynamics.%20If%20Ram%20Rajya%20is%20to%20be%20revived%2C%20society%20would%20need%20to%20produce%20the%20change.%20If%20the%20existence%20of%20temples%20could%20bring%20about%20change%2C%20there%20are%20innumerable%20Vishnu%20and%20Ram%20temples%20which%20should%20have%20made%20this%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%E2%80%99s%20times%20were%20simple%20%E2%80%93%20only%20a%20few%20basic%20things%20were%20required%20for%20existence.%20Can%20the%20nation%20return%20to%20that%3F%20Will%20people%20be%20willing%20to%20give%20up%20the%20huge%20number%20of%20products%20available%20for%20consumption%20in%20a%20modern%20economy%3F%20The%20earlier%20simple%20division%20of%20labour%20has%20given%20way%20to%20enormous%20specialisation%2C%20which%20even%20a%20small%20country%20cannot%20produce.%20Further%2C%20Ram%20was%20a%20king%20while%20today%20there%20is%20parliamentary%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ram%20Redoubled%3A%20Forget%20BCE%20and%20CE%2C%20Eras%20Will%20Now%20Divided%20Into%20PM%20and%20PM%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fram-redoubled-forget-bce-and-ce-eras-will-now-divided-into-pm-and-pm%5C%22%3ERam%20Redoubled%3A%20Forget%20BCE%20and%20CE%2C%20Eras%20Will%20Now%20Divided%20Into%20PM%20and%20PM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20globalised%20world%2C%20global%20influences%20have%20been%20willingly%20embraced%20by%20Indians.%20Skilled%20Indians%20and%20youth%20are%20migrating%20abroad%20in%20large%20numbers%20and%20rich%20Indians%20are%20taking%20out%20their%20capital%20from%20a%20country%20that%20is%20short%20of%20capital.%20The%20ongoing%20globalisation%20has%20made%20Indians%20consumerist%2C%20self-centred%2C%20atomised%2C%20greedy%20and%20amoral.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20rulers%20see%20nothing%20remiss%20in%20the%20subjugation%20of%20the%20weak%20and%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20the%20marginal.%20This%20cannot%20be%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20just%20society%20or%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Rajya%E2%80%99.%20Will%20faith%20in%20Ram%20change%20the%20ruling%20elite%E2%80%99s%20entrenched%20basic%20thinking%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20there%20be%20Ram%20Rajya%20just%20in%20India%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20global%20trends%20of%20consumerism%20and%20climate%20change%3F%20Earlier%20this%20debate%20was%20regarding%20communism%20in%20one%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20placing%20complete%20faith%20in%20Ram%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CRam%20is%20not%20fire%2C%20Ram%20is%20energy%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cembodiment%20of%20human%20values%20and%20highest%20ideals%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20wavered%20and%20appealed%20to%20people%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20grand%20temple%20of%20Shri%20Ram%20has%20been%20built%2C%20what%20next%3F%E2%80%9D%20He%20exhorted%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20lay%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20India%20of%20the%20next%20thousand%20years%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20we%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20rise%20above%20the%20self.%20%E2%80%A6The%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20will%20become%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20grand%20India%2C%20a%20developed%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20Ram%20Rajya%20will%20not%20automatically%20come%20about%20because%20%E2%80%9CRam%20is%20all%20pervasive%2C%20the%20world%2C%20the%20universal%20soul%E2%80%9D.%20The%20project%20will%20require%20a%20huge%20societal%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20broadest%20conception%2C%20it%20would%20require%20justice%20for%20all%20to%20enable%20a%20civilised%20existence.%20Equity%20among%20genders%2C%20castes%20and%20communities%20would%20have%20to%20be%20created.%20At%20a%20minimum%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20employment%20at%20a%20living%20wage%20for%20all%2C%20high%20quality%20education%20and%20health%20for%20all%2C%20and%20a%20clean%20environment.%20Today%2C%20India%20is%20even%20regressing%20from%20this%20ideal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWould%20a%20Maryada%20Purush%20have%20ever%20accepted%20the%20current%20state%20of%20affairs%20in%20the%20nation%2C%20with%20the%20rulers%20showing%20indifference%20to%20the%20plight%20of%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20people%3F%20The%20government%20controlled%20by%20the%20ruling%20elite%20can%20change%20this%20trajectory.%20If%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhavya%20ayojan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(grand%20event)%20had%20any%20impact%2C%20it%20should%20have%20been%20on%20the%20elite%20attendees%20%E2%80%93%20since%20they%20can%20bring%20about%20social%20transformation%20by%20changing%20their%20behaviour%20and%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEssential%20change%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20big%20business%2C%20and%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20its%20representatives%2C%20change%20its%20exploitative%20nature%20and%20reduce%20its%20greed%20to%20make%20businesses%20more%20ethical%3F%20Like%20checking%20monopolistic%20and%20oligopolistic%20pricing%2C%20which%20would%20lower%20prices%20for%20all.%20They%20exercise%20enormous%20control%20over%20the%20political%20leaders%20and%20the%20parties.%20So%2C%20while%20themselves%20stopping%20the%20generation%20black%20incomes%2C%20they%20could%20influence%20the%20leadership%20to%20check%20its%20growth.%20This%20is%20the%20single%20biggest%20cause%20of%20policy%20failure%2C%20since%20expenditures%20do%20not%20lead%20to%20outcomes.%20It%20reduces%20tax%20collection%2C%20resulting%20in%20shortage%20of%20funds%20for%20essential%20services%20(like%20education%20and%20health)%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20more%20civilised%20and%20peaceful%20society.%20They%20could%20pay%20their%20workers%20a%20living%20wage%20to%20raise%20their%20living%20standard.%20They%20could%20stop%20advertising%20targeted%20at%20children%20which%20turns%20them%20into%20consumerists%20and%20stop%20selling%20products%20that%20are%20harmful%20to%20children%2C%20like%20cold%20drinks%20and%20junk%20food.%20They%20could%20open%20hundreds%20of%20schools%20and%20colleges%20for%20free%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersonalities%20from%20the%20world%20of%20entertainment%20were%20present%20in%20large%20numbers.%20Through%20advertising%20they%20promote%20sales%20of%20jewellery%2C%20cold%20drinks%2C%20junk%20food%2C%20dodgy%20financial%20products%2C%20etc.%20By%20refusing%20to%20promote%20them%2C%20they%20could%20dent%20consumerism%20which%20would%20help%20socially%20as%20well%20as%20environmentally.%20They%20could%20also%20refuse%20to%20act%20in%20films%20that%20create%20social%20discord%20or%20promote%20violence%20and%20act%20only%20in%20socially%20sensitive%20films.%20They%20could%20also%20use%20their%20public%20image%20to%20exhort%20people%20to%20take%20a%20stand%20on%20pressing%20social%20issues%20and%20injustice.%20Many%20of%20them%20have%20bought%20expensive%20properties%20in%20Dubai%2C%20London%2C%20New%20York%2C%20etc.%2C%20that%20drain%20national%20resources.%20Could%20they%20bring%20their%20money%20back%3F%20Further%2C%20they%20could%20also%20refuse%20to%20accept%20black%20payments%20for%20their%20films%20and%20advertisements%2C%20whether%20in%20India%20or%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22A%20Time%20of%20Contempt%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fa-time-of-contempt%5C%22%3EA%20Time%20of%20Contempt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20members%20of%20the%20judiciary%20and%20bureaucracy%20present%20at%20the%20event%20could%20emulate%20Maryada%20Purush%20and%20uphold%20their%20independence%20in%20implementing%20rules%20rather%20than%20bending%20to%20diktats%20from%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20leaders%20present%20at%20the%20programme%20could%20choose%20to%20fight%20honest%20elections%2C%20not%20take%20tainted%20money%20and%20not%20practice%20caste%20and%20community%20vote%20bank%20politics.%20They%20could%20stop%20making%20false%20promises%2C%20disband%20their%20troll%20armies%20and%20stop%20spreading%20falsehoods%20about%20their%20opponents.%20They%20could%20stop%20pressurising%20the%20bureaucracy%20to%20bend%20rules.%20Can%20the%20rulers%20emulate%20Ram%20in%20how%20he%20respected%20criticism%20and%20cared%20about%20minority%20opinion%2C%20even%20at%20great%20personal%20cost%2C%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3Edhobi%3C%2Fem%3E%20episode%20illustrates%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEstablishing%20Ram%20Rajya%20is%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Indian%20ruling%20elite.%20But%20it%20will%20not%20happen%20by%20simply%20invoking%20Ram.%20They%20would%20have%20to%20rise%20above%20the%20self.%20Then%20only%20will%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfoundation%20of%20the%20India%20of%20the%20next%20thousand%20years%E2%80%9D%20be%20laid.%20Then%20only%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20will%20become%20a%20witness%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20grand%20India%2C%20a%20developed%20India%E2%80%9D.%20There%20have%20been%20many%20false%20starts%20in%20the%20last%2075%20years%3B%20let%20this%20not%20become%20another%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArun%20Kumar%20retired%20as%20professor%20of%20economics%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%20He%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3EUnderstanding%20Black%20Economy%20and%20Black%20Money%20in%20India%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706417854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16165842%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-16-at-4.52.24-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22origi