Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20has%20been%20no%20reaction%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20over%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20senior%20outgoing%20official%20of%20the%20Trudeau%20administration%20on%20this%20ostensible%20change%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20position.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndian%20NSA%E2%80%99s%20role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThomas%20specifically%20noted%20that%20her%20discussions%20with%20her%20counterpart%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20security%20advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20were%20positive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20RCMP%20investigation%20is%20well%20underway%20and%20so%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20speak%20too%20much%20about%20it.%20The%20RCMP%20will%20hopefully%20be%20able%20to%20prosecute%20the%20individuals%20accountable%20and%20responsible.%20But%20my%20discussions%20with%20my%20counterpart%20in%20India%20have%20been%20fruitful%20and%20I%20think%20they%E2%80%99ve%20moved%20things%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20stated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20had%20changed%2C%20Thomas%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20very%20much%20an%20evolution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Trudeau%20made%20the%20explosive%20accusations%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%2C%20India%20had%20reacted%20angrily%2C%20describing%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cabsurd%E2%80%9D.%20Subsequently%2C%20both%20nations%20expelled%20a%20senior%20diplomat%20each.%20India%20took%20additional%20measures%20by%20suspending%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%2C%20a%20restriction%20that%20was%20lifted%20after%20a%20month.%20Additionally%2C%20Canada%20was%20compelled%20to%20withdraw%20more%20than%2040%20diplomats%20as%20India%20insisted%20on%20parity%20on%20diplomatic%20presence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20government%20also%20insisted%20publicly%20that%20the%20main%20issue%20with