ration%2C%20and%20of%20NSA%20Doval%2C%20specifically.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20working%20with%20us%2C%20and%20my%20counterpart%20in%20particular%20far%20more%20closely%20to%20resolve%20this%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20senior%20Trudeau%20government%20official%20had%20said%20that%20it%20was%20important%20to%20resolve%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20but%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20relations%20with%20India%20was%20important.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20that%20we%20resolve%20what%20happened%20to%20a%20Canadian%20citizen.%20But%20we%20have%20to%20have%20people%20to%20people%20ties.%20We%20have%20a%20huge%20diaspora.%20Again%2C%20we%20have%20to%20have%20a%20trade%20relationship.%20Our%20ability%20to%20function%20in%20the%20Indo%20Pacific%20does%20rely%20on%20ha%20having%20a%20healthy%20relationship%20with%20India.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20we%20are%20working%20back%20towards%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706373617000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19140300%2FF6XA2MyWQAAYBoQ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-canada-national-security-adviser-nijjar-canada%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jody%20Thomas%20mentioned%20NSA%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20specifically%20%E2%80%93%20'India%20is%20working%20with%20us%2C%20and%20my%20counterpart%20in%20particular%20far%20more%20closely%20to%20resolve%20this.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-canada-national-security-adviser-nijjar-canada%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20would%20win%20war%20faster%20if%20it%20could%20fire%20British%20weapons%20into%20Russia%2C%20head%20of%20navy%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706369940000%2C