0feel%20that%20their%20elected%20leaders%20do%20not%20represent%20them%2C%20but%20are%20actually%20serving%20something%E2%80%A6%20else%3F%20These%20young%20people%20do%20not%20get%20to%20engage%20in%20reasoned%20debate%20with%20their%20governments.%20Instead%2C%20we%20find%20their%20leaders%20shifting%20focus%20to%20avoid%20seeing%20them.%20And%20droning%20on%20the%20same%20tired%20old%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31142124%2F49385735692_4765a99cb8_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31142124%2F49385735692_4765a99cb8_c.jpg%20799w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31142124%2F49385735692_4765a99cb8_c-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682690%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22532%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20mother%20and%20child%20in%20Gaza%2C%20before%20the%20attack.%20Photo%3A%20Catholic%20Church%20England%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0%20DEED%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20reasons%20offered%20is%20enough%20to%20explain%20the%20response%20of%20Western%20leaders%20and%20governments%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20onslaught%20on%20Gaza.%20Loyal%20support%20for%20their%20base%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%3F%20The%20Gazan%20gas%20fields%3F%20The%20Ben%20Gurion%20Canal%20they%20want%20to%20build%20via%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Aqaba%20through%20the%20center%20of%20Gaza%3F%20Guilt%20about%20the%20Holocaust%3F%20Profits%20for%20the%20arms%20industry%3F%20The%20Israel%20Lobby%20in%20the%20West%3F%20That%20they%20were%20all%20once%20settler%20colonials%20themselves%3F%20Blackmail%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20singularity%20of%20their%20response%2C%20as%20they%20strain%20at%20an%20invisible%20leash%2C%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20something%20bigger%2C%20a%20force%20outside%20of%20human%20logic.%20Because%20these%20leaders%20are%20doggedly%20set%20on%20a%20suicide%20course%2C%20risking%20reputations%20carefully%20built%20back%20after%20their%20days%20as%20settler%20colonials%20when%20they%20stand%20together%20to%20block%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza.%20They%20look%20helpless%2C%20often%20tongue-tied.%20They%20look%20like%20figureheads.%20Telegenic.%20Convenient.%20Compliant.%20And%20whoever%20else%20we%20may%20find%20on%20the%20slate%20to%20vote%20for%20can%20only%20be%20people%20like%20them.%20Anyone%20else%20with%20independent%20ideas%20will%20be%20scuttled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20the%20System%20talking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20often%20speak%20of%20%E2%80%98the%20System%E2%80%99%20as%20something%20bigger%20than%20us%2C%20but%20we%20still%20tend%20to%20see%20it%20as%20a%20collection%20of%20like-minded%20individuals%2C%20individuals%20with%20power%2C%20and%20common%20interests.%20What%20I%20am%20suggesting%20now%20is%20that%20a%20system%20as%20powerful%20as%20the%20modern%20capitalist%20system%20is%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20just%20a%20few%20individuals%20with%20power.%20It%20has%20a%20vitality%2C%20and%20a%20will%20of%20its%20own.%20Like%20Aunt%20Hillary%2C%20or%20the%20human%20brain%2C%20or%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20it%20is%20a%20higher-level%20entity%2C%20alive%20in%20its%20own%20right.%20By%20defining%20it%20as%20%E2%80%98alive%E2%80%99%20we%20can%20ask%20ourselves%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20question.%20Can%20a%20higher-level%20system%20have%20preferences%20the%20way%20humans%20do%3F%20Does%20it%20have%20an%20instinct%20for%20self-preservation%3F%20And%20are%20its%20objectives%20necessarily%20the%20same%20as%20our%20human%20objectives%3F%20Is%20it%20on%20our%20side%20at%20all%3F%20Do%20humans%20have%20any%20power%20to%20control%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Aunt%20Hillary%2C%20it%20has%20no%20problem%20offering%20up%20some%20of%20its%20own%20ants%20as%20a%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20living%20entity%2C%20it%20will%20not%20wait%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98fed%E2%80%99%2C%20like%20a%20car%2C%20or%20charged%20like%20a%20cell%20phone%2C%20but%20will%20seek%20out%20its%20preferred%20energy%20source.%20In%20this%20present%20age%20that%20would%20be%20fossil%20fuel%2C%20and%20now%20lithium%20and%20cobalt.%20And%20the%20places%20where%20these%20come%20from%20are%20now%20the%20conflict%20hotspots.%20It%20wants%20constant%20growth%20of%20the%20economy%20it%20feeds%20on.%20Being%20non-human%2C%20it%20is%20indifferent%20to%20things%20like%20religion%20and%20ethnicity%2C%20but%20it%20would%20prefer%20working%20with%20existing%20networks%20that%20run%20smoothly%2C%20respecting%20old%20communal%20fault%20lines.%20There%20is%20a%20field%20known%20as%20nonequilibrium%20thermodynamics%20which%20studies%20how%20such%20entities%20%E2%80%98come%20to%20life%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20how%20they%20fear%20entropy%20and%20demand%20total%20control.%20And%20how%20they%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20last%20issue%20is%20the%20one%20that%20interests%20me.%20Everything%20I%20see%20as%20I%20work%20on%20another%20intangible%20living%20system%2C%20language%2C%20tells%20me%20that%20it%20has%20a%20different%20tempo%20of%20evolution.%20Not%20death%2C%20as%20a%20human%20would%20experience%2C%20which%20could%20be%20gradual%20or%20sudden.%20The%20correct%20analogy%20is%20a%20species%20extinction%2C%20which%20is%20sudden%2C%20and%20is%20driven%20by%20ecological%20forces.%20The%20System%20has%20become%20unsustainable%2C%20but%20it%20cannot%20transition%20gradually%20to%20another%20which%20contradicts%20it.%20So%20it%20%E2%80%98flips%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20chaos%2C%20as%20a%20melting%20iceberg%20flips%20over%2C%20to%20become%20something%20that%20fits%20in%20with%20the%20new%20ecosystem.%20And%20we%20settle%20down%20to%20a%20new%20period%20of%20stasis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20question%20that%20excites%20people%20like%20me%20is%20how%20to%20predict%20the%20moment%20when%20a%20failed%20System%20is%20about%20to%20%E2%80%98flip%E2%80%99.%20What%20are%20the%20signs%20to%20look%20out%20for%3F%20What%20will%20happen%20as%20we%20enter%20the%20transition%20phase%3F%20I%20have%20often%20spoken%20in%20my%20online%20posts%20about%20a%20%E2%80%98shakeout%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20about%20a%20%E2%80%98great%20cull%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20System%20comes%20crashing%20down%2C%20hoping%20against%20hope%20that%20it%20will%20be%20mild.%20But%20these%20are%20only%20guesses%2C%20projections%20based%20on%20a%20catastrophic%20change%20we%20have%20seen%20in%20the%20past%20(%E2%80%98catastrophe%E2%80%99%20here%20is%20used%20in%20the%20sense%20of%20a%20sharp%20departure%20from%20what%20has%20gone%20before).%20We%20are%20still%20in%20learning%20mode%2C%20as%20we%20look%20on%20at%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20power%20shift%20taking%20shape%2C%20when%20the%20innards%20of%20the%20old%20System%20have%20become%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20is%20why%20the%20events%20in%20Gaza%20assume%20such%20Earth-shaking%20importance.%20Is%20this%20a%20%E2%80%98flip%E2%80%99%3F%20Because%20it%20may%20be%20the%20sort%20of%20watershed%20moment%20we%20have%20been%20on%20the%20lookout%20out%20for.%20People%20now%20know%20how%20much%20their%20information%2C%20their%20lives%2C%20have%20been%20curated%20up%20to%20now.%20We%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98great%20cull%E2%80%99%20too%2C%20a%20carnage%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20see%20coming%2C%20though%20we%20were%20expecting%20one%2C%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20where%20it%20would%20be.%20Now%20we%20know%20it%20is%20Gaza%20which%20has%20become%20the%20locus%20of%20the%20war%20of%20the%20worlds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20transition%20I%20dearly%20hoped%20to%20see%20in%20my%20lifetime.%20I%20had%20also%20hoped%20that%20India%20would%20play%20an%20important%20part%20in%20this%20start%20to%20a%20new%20age%2C%20but%20that%20is%20not%20to%20be.%20As%20a%20nation%2C%20we%20have%20been%20distracted%2C%20and%20have%20missed%20the%20headwinds%20that%20point%20in%20a%20new%20direction.%20The%20days%20and%20weeks%20ahead%20will%20be%20a%20time%20of%20opening%20our%20eyes%20to%20see%20beyond%20these%20dim%20present%20days%2C%20and%20to%20imagine%20a%20different%20future.%20Maybe%20there%20is%20still%20a%20chance%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPeggy%20Mohan%20is%20a%20linguist%20and%20the%20author%20of%20four%20books%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20being%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0Wanderers%2C%20Kings%2C%20Merchants%3A%20The%20Story%20of%20India%20Through%20its%20Languages%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EGurgaon%3A%20Penguin%20Random%20House%2C%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EShe%20teaches%20linguistics%20at%20Ashoka%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706363441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19092706%2FF8t8SUEWMAAvoa0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhat-explains-the-desensitisation-of-the-western-leadership-towards-horrors-in-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20singularity%20of%20its%20response%2C%20as%20it%20strains%20at%20an%20invisible%20leash%2C%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20something%20bigger%2C%20a%20force%20outside%20of%20human%20logic.%20It%20looks%20like%20figureheads%2C%20convenient%20and%20complaint.%20Anyone%20else%20with%20independent%20ideas%20will%20be%20scuttled.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhat-explains-the-desensitisation-of-the-western-leadership-towards-horrors-in-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20pauses%20funding%20to%20UN%20agency%20over%20claims%20staff%20involved%20in%20Hamas%20attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706359980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F70x70%2Fskynews-palestinians-eg