crease-7-times-in-the-next-30-years%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCurrently%252C%2520as%2520per%2520government%2520estimates%2C%252C%2520wood%252C%2520glass%252C%2520etc.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReports%20%3C%2Fa%3Esuggest%20that%20the%20percentage%20of%20MSW%20is%20anticipated%20to%20surge%20by%20sevenfold%20in%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20issue%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20staggering%20figures%20underscore%20the%20critical%20problem%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332607%2Fkerala-pharma-scientist-kenterra-low-cost-solution-waste-management-compost-apartment-complex%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20segregation%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20micro%20level.%20Records%20indicate%20that%20a%20mere%2030%20percent%20of%20waste%20undergoes%20proper%20segregation%2C%20leading%20to%20recyclable%20materials%20like%20plastic%20being%20wrongly%20disposed%20of%20in%20landfills%2C%20where%20they%20contribute%20to%20environmental%20degradation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20believe%20is%20that%20people%20need%20some%20kind%20of%20incentive%20to%20do%20something.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20concept%20where%20people%20get%20a%20reward%20for%20segregating%20their%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek%20Agarwal%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Goodeebag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoodeebag%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20waste%20management%20company%2C%20collects%20your%20segregated%20waste%20from%20your%20doorstep%20and%20provides%20reward%20points%20in%20return.%20Users%20can%20redeem%20these%20reward%20points%20to%20purchase%20groceries%20from%20the%20Goodeebag%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20icing%20on%20the%20top%3F%20All%20these%20services%20are%20free%20of%20cost!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOne%20man%E2%80%99s%20waste%20is%20another%E2%80%99s%20treasure%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20typical%20Marwa